Всем привет! Две вакансии с локацией в Киеве :flag-ua:

*Первая:* 

*Компания: Parimatch Ukraine*
*Позиция: Analytics Head*
*Локация: БЦ "Парус"*
*Вилка: 3000$ - 5000$*
*Коротко: доукомплектовать команду data и web аналитиков и сформировать стратегию развития аналитического направления. Предстоит решать задачи по всем функциональным областям компании: маркетинг, продукт, CRM, трейдинг и др.*  

*Подробно:* We are looking for:
an Analytics Manager to organize our analytics function and manage our team of analysts. You will implement tools and strategies to translate raw data into valuable business insights. In this role, we expect you to have strong logical reasoning skills and business intelligence. The ability to communicate effectively is essential. If you also have solid industry experience, we’d like to meet you. Your goal will be to help our business use data to drive high performance and quality.
Your challenge:
— Develop strategies for effective data analysis and reporting;
— Define company-wide metrics and relevant data sources;
— Select, configure and implement analytics solutions;
— Oversee all analytics operations to correct discrepancies and ensure quality;
— Extract reports from multiple sources;
— Build systems to transform raw data into actionable business insights;
— Apply industry knowledge to interpret data and improve performance;
— Keep abreast of industry news and trends.
Essential professional experience:
— Proven experience as an Analytics Manager or BI;
— Solid experience in data analysis and reporting;
— Industry experience is a plus Background in market research and project management;
— Superb communication skills;
— Analytical skills and strong organizational abilities;
— Attention to detail;
— Problem-solving aptitude;
— BSc/BA in Computer Science, Statistics, Data Management or a related field.

